{"tid":582160,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實個人頭大係好事定壞事","createTime":"2018-03-06T02:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T15:08:47.000Z","uid":167389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5269bc4be41f9805f8189d5b61b8cb4ff3da8989","tid":582160,"uid":167389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T02:37:36.000Z","msg":"話說當年老母生我嘅時候，醫生就話我個頭太大要開刀。<br />\n細細個都無咩留意造型所以都無咩問題。<br />\n一直老母都話我頭大即係聰明，雖然成績真係唔係好差（叫入到大學），不過就覺得唔係好關事嘅。<br />\n<br />\n但大個之後，特別開始注重儀容嘅時候就出事。當自己研究啲服裝/髮型造型嘅時候就發現自己點襯都好個頭太大呢樣嘢都會破壞曬。"},{"pid":"1bba9a21ff92a587ab88fea067f8acc62b7a5f03","tid":582160,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T02:38:51.000Z","msg":"頭大易寒背🤔"},{"pid":"e4426de274fcbf933c682be37c383575fb815b33","tid":582160,"uid":71496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T02:45:39.000Z","msg":"做gym<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家個膊睇返係正常<br />\n不過顯得細腳太幼<br />\n雖然以經改善左好多了"},{"pid":"220bb4be3a41a0b932a12b401675a95cdb92b7e3","tid":582160,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T02:48:54.000Z","msg":"靚仔靚女都係頭細 <br />\n個頭愈大顯得愈笨"},{"pid":"d5a4a123071cc03140c52a5c90cde45ee265baa6","tid":582160,"uid":170213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T03:09:20.000Z","msg":"個身都大理咪Match返lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e36f93b855db4c0c50c32fbfccb238a8d732e45","tid":582160,"uid":170213,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T03:10:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個身都大埋咪Match返lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4e8054c48760c4d791983def8bf33da3fc1d3b49","tid":582160,"uid":11506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T15:08:47.000Z","msg":"頭大無腦"}]}